img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下有無人都遇到咁既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你肯定唔係心理作用？</blockquote><br />\n希望係啦,不過想知點解個位元率會差咁多<br />\n明明都係無損,都係96kHz/24 bit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10415fa765a11fe882f1fd6914792eafd4a42c30","tid":402941,"uid":2280,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T20:13:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最快放歌入iPhone ge方法係咩？</blockquote><br />\niTunes"},{"pid":"3bb083927d0c036098032f7bcdc7109a6232550d","tid":402941,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T20:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最快放歌入iPhone ge方法係咩？</blockquote><br />\n我仲係用ITUNES咋,仲有更快咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff8c9f75bc251ecd2172b73b47105d76470225f","tid":402941,"uid":64481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T20:18:08.000Z","msg":"過兩日更新都聽到flac啦<br />\n仲轉乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeccd2c702193ff42f1a747b0c24f5da02b282dd","tid":402941,"uid":78326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T20:20:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用ios 版foobar 播？</blockquote><br />\n慣左用ITUNES播歌,個資料庫都儲左好多年,<br />\n用電腦聽得閒打下星,下次就自動SYNC入IPHONE"},{"pid":"a2719893dc7582db7d702645045d9b476386b116","tid":402941,"uid":120537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T20:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩搵到D High-Resolution既無損FLAC,<br />\n但用foobar轉Apple lossless, 個kbps由4622跌到3071<br />\n兩首一樣既歌比較下真係有D分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下有無人都遇到咁既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你肯定唔係心理作用？</blockquote><br />\n希望係啦,不過想知點解個位元率會差咁多<br />\n明明都係無損,都係96kHz/24 bit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nbitrate細咗因為bitrate = file size / 首歌幾長<br />\nFLAC同ALAC都係無損但有壓過，ALAC壓得好啲file細啲，咪bitrate低啲 <br />\n理論上兩個file一樣係咁多information<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以咪問你係咪心理作用 <br />\n不過其實無所謂嘅聽歌嘅嘢你開心咪得"},{"pid":"e195ae2a8742a30e41edf31659e1ba43a1f37e4c","tid":402941,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T20:29:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無 mp3 320算 乜撚野flac呀wav呀 挑 出到街都唔太覺大分別囉  用四單元我都唔覺得大分別 而家apple仲推wireless聽歌 實際分別好小</blockquote><br />\n以前都聽開320MP3,有次八卦聽下FLAC,<br />\n真係聽得出好多細節位,<br />\n感覺係好多段唔同音階既音樂打入個腦咁,<br />\n聽到每段既高位,自此返唔到轉頭<br />\n320就好似平平淡淡咁播出黎既感覺<br />\n利申,唔識聽歌,純個人感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210f1fe408ef9a94331fd68446fe1dafee639451","tid":402941,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T20:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過兩日更新都聽到flac啦<br />\n仲轉乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩上網爬文都見到,不過見自己轉左年幾歌入ITUNES,<br />\n心諗好似浪費左之前轉果D FLAC咁,上黎八卦問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075c8249a0eeeb8f85e59917b7780effe58378c3","tid":402941,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T20:43:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩搵到D High-Resolution既無損FLAC,<br />\n但用foobar轉Apple lossless, 個kbps由4622跌到3071<br />\n兩首一樣既歌比較下真係有D分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下有無人都遇到咁既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你肯定唔係心理作用？</blockquote><br />\n希望係啦,不過想知點解個位元率會差咁多<br />\n明明都係無損,都係96kHz/24 bit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nbitrate細咗因為bitrate = file size / 首歌幾長<br />\nFLAC同ALAC都係無損但有壓過，ALAC壓得好啲file細啲，咪bitrate低啲 <br />\n理論上兩個file一樣係咁多information<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以咪問你係咪心理作用 <br />\n不過其實無所謂嘅聽歌嘅嘢你開心咪得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54db7c5362565fc20cc25c5e6aaa7437f74382b","tid":402941,"uid":35667,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T20:54:16.000Z","msg":"聽歌好多時都心理作用<br />\n有人貼張貼紙落部機度都話好聽左架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd16e8f9ff21716f723a9290f7b2cf193697edd7","tid":402941,"uid":18283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T21:01:05.000Z","msg":"用vox"},{"pid":"471325e61b500972e47f36cee1498de049ad9950","tid":402941,"uid":37820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T23:53:55.000Z","msg":"Hi res 嘅alac好似冇得經itunes 拉入iphone㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然用開player聽<br />\n但都會拉少少歌入落iphone 做運動時聽<br />\n但聽44.1/16就算 因為再靚嘅歌經電話聽都係差好遠"},{"pid":"4d3da9847f4db6f6f50eb0098325a156bf29dc73","tid":402941,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:32:54.000Z","msg":"有幾多人聽得出分別"},{"pid":"b490f78decf5f5dfa8870f1f70bd0b6f7d8b7213","tid":402941,"uid":81598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:45:44.000Z","msg":"由岩岩出iTunes開始一直用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\niTunes其實好方便，唔明點解d人唔用"},{"pid":"117719a87d4103f884197be8cec4fc2ea97496c4","tid":402941,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:46:46.000Z","msg":"flac本來都有壓縮架啦"},{"pid":"9e09db16873a8bf3b3f1e31fd246f94a6d2ebb49","tid":402941,"uid":22553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:49:04.000Z","msg":"出街聽就求鳩其啦，隔到人聲咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1dcce08202955ea79ce59b663756d42302758b3","tid":402941,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T00:52:41.000Z","msg":"硬係要講應該係解碼速度唔係全首都穩定<br />\n所以聽落會懞d掛"},{"pid":"bef8a8e88996a39ae1092256f975f56b53a28dc7","tid":402941,"uid":138658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T01:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/090102_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F090102_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=45f39a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n參考返上面張圖，flac同alac個壓縮率相約，有機會係原本個flac檔唔係用lv8壓縮 你可以用foobar壓縮做lv8睇下有冇分別"},{"pid":"f985eedaedfe3b9876ce9bb088637687af69016a","tid":402941,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T02:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出街聽就求鳩其啦，隔到人聲咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最主要真係隔聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9882ff39d9ea7318bcde8abbe82880341e83196e","tid":402941,"uid":45189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T02:55:55.000Z","msg":"你真係聽得出個分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea144fac33d53194f64e47b249f3cdc1520263c","tid":402941,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:02:46.000Z","msg":"用開 itunes 聲320 mp3<br />\n跟機earphone 普普通通<br />\n換隻1000左右earphone 已經好大分別<br />\n<br />\n咁我出街聽都有其他雜音嫁啦<br />\n無損既/CD ，留返係屋企靜靜享用"},{"pid":"7729d669f5d000dba10d7887795c06e5b97427ff","tid":402941,"uid":3223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:22:22.000Z","msg":"iTunes 12.7 同 iOS 11<br />\n支援FLAC<br />\n直入"},{"pid":"1c4beb31d2a96149c58bf221a6e3b231c81b9c11","tid":402941,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:59:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由岩岩出iTunes開始一直用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\niTunes其實好方便，唔明點解d人唔用</blockquote><br />\n好用在佢跟TAG黎分類,十幾年前用WINMX搵MP3,<br />\n夠膽死個名明明寫住十面埋伏都可以播首失戀王出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後尾轉會用IPHONE,用左幾個月時間將D舊歌洗TAG改名入COVER分類<br />\n一次過拉入去,依家用個PLAYLIST SET一SET就有自己想要聽既歌<br />\n呢個先真正神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有以前IPHONE最正係個COVER FLOW,打橫係咁掃,依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29af11b87ddfe06e5701fe8bc6f126c923dd4e5","tid":402941,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:13:26.000Z","msg":"Me, 從來唔online聽歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全部入晒機聽！我都覺自己怪怪地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a69f2cf3b7fbfa9f706b990099e6588e83fced","tid":402941,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:27:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hi res 嘅alac好似冇得經itunes 拉入iphone㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然用開player聽<br />\n但都會拉少少歌入落iphone 做運動時聽<br />\n但聽44.1/16就算 因為再靚嘅歌經電話聽都係差好遠</blockquote><br />\n岩岩試左,真係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSO9SAD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d1582781d2f179a4d4418e4bef79c639437443","tid":402941,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>iTunes 12.7 同 iOS 11<br />\n支援FLAC<br />\n直入</blockquote><br />\n我依家ITUNES係12.7,但係佢唔俾我拉入去.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7b5e55a7ef47c0917a0544be30dbc0a533a439","tid":402941,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:35:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/090102_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F090102_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=45f39a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n參考返上面張圖，flac同alac個壓縮率相約，有機會係原本個flac檔唔係用lv8壓縮 你可以用foobar壓縮做lv8睇下有冇分別</blockquote><br />\n上網睇話咩LEVEL愈細,即係壓縮程度愈細,個FILE SIZE就愈大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過算啦,原來就算壓做ALAC都入唔到IPHONE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我首宇多田光呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17221656e3e3a1ea33ffd9bb664a2858c690c46","tid":402941,"uid":16461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:38:35.000Z","msg":"IPhone播無損9成係心理作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係想聽曬無損，不如買個Player聽啦，輸出差好遠，就算Filo嗰啲入門級數嘅Player都同IPhone差好遠"},{"pid":"afedf42ba05f57cebcfb35cafdd8fb99b7ed659f","tid":402941,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:38:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用開 itunes 聲320 mp3<br />\n跟機earphone 普普通通<br />\n換隻1000左右earphone 已經好大分別<br />\n<br />\n咁我出街聽都有其他雜音嫁啦<br />\n無損既/CD ，留返係屋企靜靜享用</blockquote><br />\n本來係想屋企出街兩邊都聽得,入落ITUNES就一勞永逸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f917b056bfffc7ba66c7e0eabbfb1874f2f6c0","tid":402941,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:44:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>硬係要講應該係解碼速度唔係全首都穩定<br />\n所以聽落會懞d掛</blockquote><br />\n就好似有D位唔夠大聲咁,FLAC就每個位結尾都好大聲,有D餘音咁<br />\n希望係心理作用,其實兩首聽真D又真係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1c3643df9ff3a48598698c50a250982b652924","tid":402941,"uid":78326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:48:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Me, 從來唔online聽歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree